# rule.forbid.term.addition.synonym

## severity: blocker

do not introduce terms that duplicate established vocabulary.

## .scope

applies to new terms only. if established, defer to convention.

## .how

1. identify new terms in blueprint
2. search codebase for synonyms
3. if established term exists for same concept: flag

## blocker examples

- "client" when "customer" established
- "fetch" when "get" established

## not a blocker

- "brain" already established: defer to convention
